{"tid":535213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆乳露內褲引不滿 紐國大媽投訢亞航空姐過份暴露","createTime":"2018-01-20T15:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T17:12:48.000Z","uid":157545,"like":724,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"c70eb923857b7dc89170cd895d26856f308c88a0","tid":535213,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180120/640_a83de350f790d275ca9747f403001f40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180120%2F640_a83de350f790d275ca9747f403001f40.jpg&h=26db0631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前馬來西亞媒體報導指出，一名紐西蘭大媽上書大馬國會議員，說她搭飛機看到空姐穿著暴露、爆乳又露內褲，讓她極為憤怒，原來這位大媽所抱怨的空姐，就是亞洲航空(Air Asia)的空姐。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，紐西蘭大媽羅本森(June Robertson)自稱「中年專業大媽」，但她批評亞航空姐制服只會損害馬來西亞的名聲，因為她曾在吉隆坡第二國際機場的商場內，看到有空姐蹲下露出內褲。還有她搭乘飛機時，看到空姐穿爆乳制服，當空姐彎腰低頭時，馬上就露出那「凶狠的事業線」，讓她完全不能接受，還要求空姐把外套扣子扣上。<br />\n<br />\n羅本森說，她愛大馬，在過去10年當中，平均每年都會到馬來西亞兩次，但她不懂為何這家航空公司的空姐裙子要穿得這麼短，讓她覺得被冒犯，而且歐美、紐澳的空姐制服，都不會這樣穿。羅本森還說，她喜歡大馬的原因，是因為大馬人都會互相尊重，且女性的穿著不像妓女，但她不懂為何政府允許航空公司讓空姐穿成這樣。<br />\n<br />\n亞航對於羅本森的投訴，則是沒有多做評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180120/640_9685472117d1fa77a49e9f643db2872f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180120%2F640_9685472117d1fa77a49e9f643db2872f.jpg&h=55e25b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180120/640_1d3ae472d05ce0273174828e81ed8e4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180120%2F640_1d3ae472d05ce0273174828e81ed8e4e.jpg&h=1dbc37b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有邊間制服正過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2009b5cbbbd64c032d02ee8a898aafc04368b7","tid":535213,"uid":13724,"like":194,"dislike":8,"score":186,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"Air Asia 啲女又真係幾正"},{"pid":"dceb3c83f82bed120943da86ca88d091506d8e20","tid":535213,"uid":154756,"like":3,"dislike":27,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"全部我既"},{"pid":"6533d40d109352fef83709e295f3de82faa2c594","tid":535213,"uid":828,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0628989eee41b24f5aae2604c3ba671d0e51f74d","tid":535213,"uid":22736,"like":272,"dislike":8,"score":264,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"自己冇就要人都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d029099afea01c6abd884f2347f9ecafc6ec26b6","tid":535213,"uid":28113,"like":202,"dislike":6,"score":196,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 葡萄就葡萄啦"},{"pid":"669ae7be716c3e5fd9e1299db7533ef2a7dc80cb","tid":535213,"uid":116131,"like":288,"dislike":13,"score":275,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"俾人叫飛雞係有原因，番工條裙短到露埋底褲都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走哂光都唔覺有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4064036c778d5823f863b6fe9a4164a047d05f","tid":535213,"uid":12736,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"一烏低身放餐乜都睇曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkg